                <CardHeader>
                  <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <div>
                      <CardTitle as="h2" id="detail-heading" className="text-lg">
                        ご利用明細
                      </CardTitle>
                      <CardDescription>
                        {period.label}・{period.charges.length} 件
                      </CardDescription>
                    </div>
                    {period.charges.length > 0 && (
                      <Badge variant="outline" className="tabular-nums">
                        新規ご利用 {yen(newChargesTotal)}
                      </Badge>
                    )}
                  </div>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <StatementTable charges={period.charges} />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </section>

            {/* --- Single GaugeChart, used as a compact a11y demo of the --- */}
            {/* --- one-arc gauge for "今月の予算消化" (budget burn). --- */}
            {period.charges.length > 0 && (
              <section aria-labelledby="budget-heading">
                <Card>
                  <CardHeader>
                    <CardTitle as="h2" id="budget-heading" className="text-lg">
                      今月のご利用ペース
                    </CardTitle>
                    <CardDescription>
                      月のご利用目安 {yen(200_000)} に対する消化状況
                    </CardDescription>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent className="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
                    <GaugeChart
                      value={newChargesTotal}
                      min={0}
                      max={200_000}
                      label="今月のご利用"
                      color={newChargesTotal > 200_000 ? "destructive" : "primary"}
                      formatValue={(v) => formatCurrency(v)}
                      rangeLabel="ご利用目安"
                    />
                    <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground tabular-nums">
                      {formatPercent(Math.min(newChargesTotal / 200_000, 1))} 消化
                    </p>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </section>
            )}

            <p className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">
              ※ 表示金額・手数料はサンプルデータに基づく目安です。実際のご請求額とは異なる場合があります。
            </p>
          </>
        )}
      </Container>
    </main>
  );
}

